						               													<description>&amp;quot;Verge Of War&amp;quot; is a Sci-Fi wargame with 28mm resin miniatures set in the original VergeOfWar Universe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The opening campaign is dedicated to the first clash of Human forces and Seit, the race of mighty psionics and insidious intriguers, at the edge of human-inhabited space. The forces of the Human fleet conducted a routine raid against pirates in the sector but discovered that they were not alone in the universe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In total, there are 10 factions in the game &amp;ndash; Human Empire, The Seit Civilization,&amp;#10;Pirates, The Asgar, The Kja Kingdoms, Eltofa, Rungars, Skrags, Triclons, Arachnids.&amp;#10;Each faction has its own history, political structure, physiological characteristics,&amp;#10;hierarchy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Verge Of War is a classical wargame with RPG elements. The game uses&amp;#10;six-sided dice, D6. Before the battle begins, your commander chooses skills from&amp;#10;three sets that reflect different strategies, doctrines or military specialties. Each set&amp;#10;is divided into 10 levels, which reflect the experience and expertise of your&amp;#10;commander. A typical game consists of 6 game rounds and takes about 30-120&amp;#10;minutes depending on the size of the armies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has flexible mechanics and balanced rules that are easy to learn.&amp;#10;Build your army, conquer the galaxy and make your commander hero famous all over the world! &amp;#10;Achieve immortality!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;THE FUTURE IS UNCERTAIN...YOU SHAPE IT!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
